name: Roy Tang
text: Er, parang weird na ang cinite mo is an article where one town is thinking about charging $300 for 911 calls. I went ahead and just checked wikipedia, usually daw may state-level fees  https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/9-1-1#Funding_9-1-1_services  Mukhang nde sya yung tipong maccharge ka when you make a call, that's what I assumed when you said nde sya free
